snippet.title: Session - Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/861650/Session_Skateboarding_Sim_Game

If you listen to those lyrics, skaters aren't that different! 

It's time for you to follow the way to where they are the same as you! 

Session is now available on Steam for PC!! Keep an eye out for the Xbox Game Preview which is currently targeted for October 2019.

#sessiongame #sesh
